The http://www.constitutionparty.com/ Constitution Party, also known as the American Independent Party (AIP) in California, is a national political party. According to a May 2008 report from the Yolo County elections office, the city of Davis has 520 registered AIP members, or 1.49% of registered voters.Footnote(Yolo County Elections Office. http://www.yoloelections.org/voting/stats/sfiles/052208%20report%20of%20registration.pdf Report of Registration  State Reporting Districts. 20080522.)

Currently, no local representatives are members of the AIP.
